the kitchen and you knew you could make 300 cookies in a day,

43

00:03:04,120  -->  00:03:05,660
but not a cookie more.

44

00:03:05,660  -->  00:03:08,000
Or perhaps your budget only allows for

45

00:03:08,000  -->  00:03:12,240
a certain number of cookies to be made before you start losing money.

46

00:03:12,240  -->  00:03:16,760
You could set a limit to prevent an overage with an upper bound.

47

